response.original_title: NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017: Day 6
response.overview: On October 25, 2017, Hachinohe City Higashi Gymnasium in Hachinohe hosted NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017.  The main event featured Los Ingobernables de Japon (BUSHI, EVIL, Hiromu Takahashi, SANADA & Tetsuya Naito) vs CHAOS (Gedo, Kazuchika Okada, SHO, Tomohiro Ishii & YOH).  The card also featured Suzuki-gun (El Desperado, Taichi & TAKA Michinoku) vs Dragon Lee, Tiger Mask & Titan.  Other wrestlers on the show include David Finlay, Juice Robinson and Kota Ibushi, and more!
response.title: NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017: Day 6
